---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Saachi K Gupta" showHero={true}>
  <div style="max-width: 60ch; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem;">
    <p style="margin: 0;">💻 <strong>I build the teams, processes, and strategy that turn complex bets into repeatable results.</strong> My work sits at the intersection of commercial strategy, financial rigor, and technical complexity — across consumer and enterprise monetization, strategic partnerships, and operations at scale.</p>
    <p style="margin: 0;">At Amazon: financial architect of enterprise partnerships with Disney, Wynn, Northwell, and Greystar. Built quarterly operating plan infrastructure for 25+ teams. Deployed 150K+ Alexa devices in hospitals and senior living during COVID. <strong>I can create the model and read the room.</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 0;">🤝 Building <strong>community</strong> matters to me - through SheJumps, Amazon's finance rotational programs, and student organizations I led at Wharton and UChicago. <strong>I hold an MBA from Wharton (Operations & Finance) and a BA in Economics & Political Science from the University of Chicago.</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 0;">🚴 Outside of work, you'll find me backpacking, training for triathlons, scuba diving, or working on craft projects.</p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 4px;">
      <a href="/resume.pdf" download="SaachiKGupta_Resume.pdf" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(31,28,24,0.18); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--accent-strong); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; background: rgba(255,252,246,0.7); transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(63,95,74,0.08)';this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)';"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,252,246,0.7)';this.style.borderColor='rgba(31,28,24,0.18)';">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="width:16px;height:16px;flex-shrink:0;" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.625 1.5H9a3.75 3.75 0 013.75 3.75v1.875c0 1.036.84 1.875 1.875 1.875H16.5a3.75 3.75 0 013.75 3.75v7.875c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 01-1.875-1.875V3.375c0-1.036.84-1.875 1.875-1.875zm6.905 9.97a.75.75 0 00-1.06 0l-3 3a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06l1.72-1.72V18a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-4.19l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06l-3-3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/><path d="M14.25 5.25a5.23 5.23 0 00-1.279-3.434 9.768 9.768 0 016.963 6.963A5.23 5.23 0 0016.5 7.5h-1.875a.375.375 0 01-.375-.375V5.25z"/></svg>
        Resume
      </a>
      <a href="/exec-bio.pdf" download="SaachiKGupta_ExecutiveBio.pdf" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(31,28,24,0.18); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--accent-strong); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; background: rgba(255,252,246,0.7); transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(63,95,74,0.08)';this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)';"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,252,246,0.7)';this.style.borderColor='rgba(31,28,24,0.18)';">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="width:16px;height:16px;flex-shrink:0;" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.625 1.5H9a3.75 3.75 0 013.75 3.75v1.875c0 1.036.84 1.875 1.875 1.875H16.5a3.75 3.75 0 013.75 3.75v7.875c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 01-1.875-1.875V3.375c0-1.036.84-1.875 1.875-1.875zm6.905 9.97a.75.75 0 00-1.06 0l-3 3a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06l1.72-1.72V18a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-4.19l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06l-3-3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/><path d="M14.25 5.25a5.23 5.23 0 00-1.279-3.434 9.768 9.768 0 016.963 6.963A5.23 5.23 0 0016.5 7.5h-1.875a.375.375 0 01-.375-.375V5.25z"/></svg>
        Executive Bio
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</SiteLayout>
